1331
01:44:53,006 --> 01:44:55,175
É! Vai, Dogs!

1332
01:44:55,592 --> 01:44:57,052
Quer me derrubar?

1333
01:45:00,597 --> 01:45:03,182
É, corra como uma vadia!

1334
01:45:03,496 --> 01:45:05,393
Quer dançar, garoto?

1335
01:45:13,860 --> 01:45:15,237
A corrida acabou, Chuck.

1336
01:45:20,700 --> 01:45:23,203
-Ren, Ren, cuidado!
-Jogue justo, punk!

1337
01:45:27,541 --> 01:45:29,125
Graças ao Sr. Beamis.

1338
01:45:29,126 --> 01:45:31,710
